race.comment: Competitive. THE MOUNT (3) has returned to racing in good order with narrow defeats at Warrnambool and Colac last time as a $2.7F. Fitter again and he can take this out. THE MARINER (4) is fast and folded up at Colac at the same day. Led beaten a nose in a Naracoorte 66 prior and that reads well. Keeps the handy 3kg claim and is worth another chance. FREDERICK (1) was back on track winning a 52 comfortably at Kerang bet a 3.3F. Has an awkward barrier today but is a chance to repeat. FROSTY NIGHT (7) was a determined winner two back at Terang. Less effective last time when fading but. Also draws out but is good enough to consider.
